{"tid":571083,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"修煉","createTime":"2018-02-24T10:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T11:14:38.000Z","uid":40867,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c31e2b641af355c5217dfaefd1f010d471d60ff","tid":571083,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"依家呢個世界物質太豐富<br />\n太容易滿足<br />\n<br />\n所以今日開始實行一系列修煉<br />\n<br />\n第一項<br />\n唔打飛機兩個禮拜(次次都一個禮拜冇乜意思)<br />\n<br />\n第二項 <br />\n唔上fb ig 等等垃圾資訊發放地兩個禮拜<br />\n搭車悶最多都上bbc睇新聞同增強下英文能力<br />\n連登只上呢個post update下<br />\n<br />\n第三項<br />\n每晚睡前冥想 修復大腦同時反思一日所做<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多<br />\n三項同期執行<br />\n盡我一切能力唔破戒 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打都想修煉下自己 或者有咩認真嘅建議"},{"pid":"79778cf7039cb904ae991b33192f1edfa8d28315","tid":571083,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"唔上連登"},{"pid":"63a49ece064449b76e5bbcbedc0229895297b820","tid":571083,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79778cf7039cb904ae991b33192f1edfa8d28315","tid":571083,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"唔上連登"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"唔會上 得呢個post會跟進下"},{"pid":"f88da5fe882bfe7fe785c9d78ea0d736742a101d","tid":571083,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"食齋"},{"pid":"73dc84c52478d638fa59d0c6d0918c1221a39e5b","tid":571083,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f88da5fe882bfe7fe785c9d78ea0d736742a101d","tid":571083,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"食齋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"最近因為突然爆濕疹 少食肉好多 醫生話濕毒<br />\n<br />\n不過做唔到全齋 但相對地已經冇乜肉類"},{"pid":"2292559d186c160b018c96f32c28b32ac9458ff7","tid":571083,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"我諗應該新增一項<br />\n<br />\n早睡早起<br />\n尋晚都